DeleteBook(uint256).details: Emitted when a book is deleted from the library.

NewBook(uint256).details: Emitted when a new book is added to the library. Note `bookId` starts from 0.

NewRental(uint256,uint256).details: Emitted when a new book rental is made. Note `trackingId` and `bookId` start from 0.

addBook(string,string,uint256).details: Add a Book with predefined `name`, `description` and `price` to the library. Returns a boolean value indicating whether the operation succeeded. Emits a {NewBook} event.

borrowBook(uint256,uint256,uint256).details: Borrow a book has `_bookId`. The rental period starts from `startTime` ends with `endTime`. Returns a boolean value indicating whether the operation succeeded. Emits a `NewRental` event.

deleteBook(uint256).details: Delete a book from the library. Only the book's owner or the library's owner is authorised for this operation. Returns a boolean value indicating whether the operation succeeded. Emits a `DeleteBook` event.
